WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:00.032
He won't give it to me,
and he says there's no chance.

00:00:03.560 --> 00:00:05.516
Sonny?

00:00:06.440 --> 00:00:07.714
Sonny?

00:00:10.520 --> 00:00:12.954
(KNOCK AT DOOR)

00:00:13.840 --> 00:00:15.671
Sonny?

00:00:15.880 --> 00:00:18.553
- Sonny, are you in there?
- What?

00:00:18.760 --> 00:00:20.159
The old man wants you.

00:00:21.560 --> 00:00:23.391
One minute.

00:00:24.600 --> 00:00:26.591
(SEX RESUMES)

